title: Tanya Burr & Jim Chapman head home for Christmas
text:
Tanya Burr and Jim Chapman to turn on Norwich Christmas lights Credit: Ian West/Press Association Norfolk's celebrity YouTubers Tanya Burr and Jim Chapman will be turning on the Christmas lights in Norwich this year.
The newly-married couple will be in the city centre for the big switch-on on Thursday 19th November.
More than 3 million people follow the pair online. Tanya, who grew up in Norwich, made her name with online make-up and style tutorials.
Tanya Burr has more than 1.6m followers on Twitter Credit: Dominic Lipinski/PA Her new husband, who grew up near Attleborough and studied at the University of East Anglia, is a fashion writer.
Jim Chapman has more than 1.5 million followers on Twitter Credit: Doug Peters/EMPICS Entertainment Last updated Tue 20 Oct 2015 Entertainment Norfolk
